# Atlas test workflow

Atlas uses dependency-free Node.js tooling. Prefer the scripts documented in `README.md` and
`package.json`.

Common commands:

- `npm run lint`
- `npm run validate:records`
- `npm run verify:migrations`
- `npm test`

Use the narrowest relevant test command first. Run the broader suite when changes cross package,
API, fixture, migration, or workflow boundaries.

Changed behavior should include tests. If a change is documentation/configuration only, add a
lightweight integration test when the workflow contract should remain stable.

